\pc \bd 214\bd*

\s Nikifika kwake Bwana
\zon1 4
\zoli1 \bd Nikifika kwake Bwana, yeye Mukombozi wangu, Na sikumutumikia hata siku moja hapa\bd*\bd ?\bd*
\pc \bdit Nitakwenda kukutana naye na mikono bule, Bila tunda hata moja\bdit*\bdit ?\bdit*\bdit  Itakuwa haya kubwa\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Hata siogopi kufa, kitu ninachoogopa Ni kufika kwake Bwana bila nafsi hata moja.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nitakwenda kukutana naye na mikono bule, Bila tunda hata moja? Itakuwa haya kubwa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Siku nyingi nimeishi bila kumutumikia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Zimepita\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd zote bule, zimepita kwa milele\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Nitakwenda kukutana naye na mikono bule, Bila tunda hata moja? Itakuwa haya kubwa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ee wapenzi, musimame, mutumike kila siku, Mutafute wapotevu, muwalete kwa milele\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Nitakwenda kukutana naye na mikono bule, Bila tunda hata moja? Itakuwa haya kubwa.\bdit*
